Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:07.82,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:15.45,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:22.54,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I closed my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:29.00,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,and distanced myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:35.76,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,5 PM in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:42.43,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:50.11,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:54.07,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:58.49,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:06.58,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:13.80,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:21.14,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:27.90,song-op,,0000,0000,0000,,and we understand each other.
