Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:44.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:45.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:46.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.05,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,One..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:53.36,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,- Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,- Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:02:01.33,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, younger Matsunaga. My class isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.37,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna go home too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:10.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Where your loved one waits for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.01,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:14.31,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Rika-san is so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.64,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'd like to go see my loved one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:28.08,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you want to go see your loved one. Fine, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.69,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Loved one? What did you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:40.08,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,No improper conduct with opposite sex! Stop, younger Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:48.55,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,So she used teleport. I'll catch them some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.42,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a taxi service.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.29,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So don't think I can come whenever you call me up with telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:00.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.55,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So you gonna visit him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:18.03,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You bet. He's so happy to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.70,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But I think he might get annoyed if you go every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.43,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. He told me my cooking's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.67,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I made too many fried squid rings. You can have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.26,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, how does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:40.73,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh good. Would you try niku-jaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a4}Note: Niku-Jaga = beef and potato stew
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.52,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Niku-jaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.58,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I see what you meant by first time. It's got a very fresh taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:10.27,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Kurashige senpai doesn't get food poisoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.10,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:13.58,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.45,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.14,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but what about your club and other things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.78,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.59,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you more food tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:31.74,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.49,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.56,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,She was so pretty. Who was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.89,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's Kurashige-senpai's sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:36.11,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It's 'cause Tomomi said something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.26,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way senpai would...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.45,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.93,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get the roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.67,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,My friend came by and dropped them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:31.46,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,The blond lady? What about the sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.48,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,This one, the friend who just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.18,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Another foreign lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:47.78,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you food, but I guess you're stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:51.49,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're misunderstanding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.11,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:02.54,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:05.78,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:37.39,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Kurashige-senpai became some womanizer..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:41.47,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause, I saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.52,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:52.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just can't understand the tastes of science buff..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.46,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you taking it seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.16,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that?...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:06.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Matsunaga. Oh, Kurashige-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You want to talk to Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.64,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.59,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.54,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, you should've talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:47.92,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I should've guessed. I should've told her everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.21,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I know it was hard to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:57.33,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage's been flying high ever since you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:00.43,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,They're in Japan as exchange students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.21,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.99,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Their boyfriends in high school back in London
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:08.03,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,dumped me all the letters and gifts to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.27,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,So, I've been getting in contact with each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:16.87,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. Mikage always jumps the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.09,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.70,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.64,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So they're exchange students. Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:00.81,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:01.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll get mad at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.62,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think it's a good idea to stick around with him all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.09,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.88,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see.. Overdose of affection isn't that good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:21.11,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I think I know what you're trying to get at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:25.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I've been going high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I was too happy to see him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, what's wrong? Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:37.78,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I'll go take a batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.67,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:31.08,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's been my dream to study in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:37.92,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I got it from my relative in London. You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:45.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Isn't it important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.34,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.77,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage... Mikage?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.89,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi, did you see her too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:18.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why was she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:26.70,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:31.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.59,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye, Mikage-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.03,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai... Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.60,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.84,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Younger Matsunaga. No sleeping in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.64,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I see your nose hair sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:56.72,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to evade me! As punishment, you solve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:02.21,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You already finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:07.83,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}Not bad, Younger Matsunaga. This was from\N an entrance exam of a national university.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:17.39,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,There. I found it under your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:24.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't acting like yourself, brooding over. Can't you believe in senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.38,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, will you? To senpai's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.32,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.43,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:25.11,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! How dare you skip out class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.15,Default,teacher,0000,0000,0000,,As a punishment, you clean up the science building!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.53,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.48,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mikage Matsunaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.92,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,You got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.77,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.85,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,That Kurashige and I are in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:06.01,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Kurashige and I are just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:11.69,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,My sweetheart back in London is Kurashige's roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:16.68,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,So I was dropping by to see Kurashige to hear about my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.60,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Kurashige's worried because you misunderstood everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.10,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, Kurashige?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:37.24,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,That's not nice. Don't look so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.23,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,I brought her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.29,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:44.32,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:50.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.74,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god you found out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.75,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,So her experiments always blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:58.94,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:02.83,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Last year's club budget was used up just on repairs of the club lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:07.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to tell her everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.79,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:14.56,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Just to straighten up the fact, half of it was Kageura-sensei's explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.19,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:26.01,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,He's a really nice man, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.04,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:39.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you crying in senpai's room yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.23,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you saw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:49.80,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Harry. He loves basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.16,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,I always had to wait for the practice to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:57.30,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,After that, we always went to see movies or dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:03.06,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,I came to Japan just as Kurashige got there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.80,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,but Harry always talked about Kurashige in his letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.67,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could see the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:13.94,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,But... He hasn't written recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.40,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single letter for the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.79,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I got a call from Kurashige.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:25.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So, senpai got something from Harry for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:32.09,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I got so emotional when I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:37.64,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,So Kurashige was comforting me. I'm sorry, Mikage-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:39.87,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:44.22,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't write me, but I guess he wants me to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.24,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,Men are always so selfish, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.37,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.33,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, let's teleport to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.83,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:03.62,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go. We made it last time. We can do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.39,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna do over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.94,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go see Harry and tell him to write letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:13.41,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do what I can do for Liz-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.67,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd choke to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.08,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,So this's Kurashige-senpai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:44.74,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,This picture's just before he left for England, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he was remembering about you looking at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do? You gonna tell Liz-san about Harry-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.54,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.85,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.11,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You knew already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:42.47,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Harry started going out with her because he got lonely after Liz went to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.84,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Does Liz-san know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.90,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I'm sure she noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.38,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,She was concerned about him not writing any letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:56.58,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell her, but I couldn't get around to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.21,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.09,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Liz forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:08.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No, she left it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.31,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:19.23,Default,Tomo&Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Liz-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.04,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Have you noticed already?..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:33.70,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:40.50,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but I just couldn't give up about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.29,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I went to see Kurashige everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.08,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,But everything's OK now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Liz-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:57.27,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,I gave this to Harry as his birthday gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:02.45,Default,Liz,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write a dear John with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.53,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,So she already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.91,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be OK though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.53,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'd find a great boyfriend again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.56,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Can I keep this watch for good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.78,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what would you like for tomorrow's lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.82,Default,Kurashige,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:53.73,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to know about our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:57.45,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,And every time we see her, it's raining. She's gotta be a rain woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.38,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.35,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,"Strange Rain Passing By."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:04.01,Default,preview,0000,0000,0000,,We'll teleport to your room tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.30,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.60,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.93,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:18.15,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:34.79,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.08,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,, that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:51.60,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:58.02,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:05.07,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:11.82,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:14.74,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:20.21,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.21,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:26.67,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:29.76,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.14,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:18.15,credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ending Song\N"There has to be Both of Us"\N("Futarijanakya Dame Nano")\NBy Dio
